  <brief_title>Endoscopic Sphincterotomy vs. Balloon Dilation for Assessment of Pancreatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Endoscopic Sphincterotomy vs. Balloon Dilation for Assessment of Pancreatitis: A Prospective Randomized Multicenter Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
